How to build?
To build matrix, execute GNU make in the current directory.

How to test matrix?
I only tried it with bochs 2.4.6 and boot it with grub installed.

What architecture does matrix support now?
At this moment matrix only support the x86 architecture.

How to create an image?
dd if=/dev/zero of=matrix.img bs=512 count=2880

How to create a bochs vm using the image?
Create a file bochsrc.bxrc and write the configuration into the file. You can refer to the documents on bochs site.

How to install grub to the image?
sudo losetup /dev/loop0 ~/vm/matrix/matrix.img
sudo mkfs.msdos /dev/loop0
sudo mount /dev/loop0 /mnt
sudo grub-install --root-directory=/mnt --recheck --force /dev/loop0
